channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Harris leaves out deadly botched Afghanistan withdrawal in soaring pro-military DNC speech
item.description: Vice President Kamala Harris touted her foreign policy record and support of the military in her DNC speech, while snubbing any mention of the botched 2021 Afghanistan withdrawal.

item.title: Democratic Party revels in expected end of RFK Jr.'s campaign
item.description: Harris campaign officials aren't too worried over whether independent presidential candidate Robert F. Kennedy Jr. will stay in the race or opt to team up with former President Donald Trump, in fact, they believe it would do "nothing" to affect the race.

item.title: The Week: Kamala Accepts the Democrats’ Nomination
item.description: Plus: Candace Owens does her own research.

item.title: Marc Elias’ Footsoldier Tarnishes Watchdog Group To Keep Illegitimate Voters On Nevada’s Rolls
item.description: You have to wonder why anyone would lie to keep people on Nevada’s voter rolls who no longer live in Nevada.

item.title: Will Robert F Kennedy Jr's likely exit from 2024 race boost Trump over Harris?
item.description: How much would a Robert F. Kennedy Jr. endorsement of former President Donald Trump - if the Democrat turned independent presidential candidate ends his White House bid - impact the 2024 election with Kamala Harris?

item.title: Pro-life pregnancy centers win temporary injunction against Letitia James attacks
item.description: A federal judge has blocked New York Attorney General Letitia James from taking legal action against pro-life pregnancy centers that promote the use of progesterone to reverse the abortion-pill process, citing the threat to their free-speech rights.

item.title: Denial of democracy, &c.
item.description: On Venezuela, Israel, China, chess, Alain Delon, Chi Chi Rodriguez, and more.

item.title: Dana Bash Admits Democrats Are The Party Of Low-T Beta Males
item.description: Dana Bash characterized Democrats as an estrogen-fueled political movement uncomfortable with traditional respect for masculinity.

item.title: Harris tries to thread Israel, Gaza needle with anti-Israel agitators a constant presence at DNC
item.description: Accepting the Democratic nomination for president, Vice President Kamala Harris said she supports Israel's right to self-defense but also criticized its "devastating" toll on Gaza civilians.

item.title: RFK Jr. withdraws from Arizona ballot amid speculation of possible alliance with Trump
item.description: Robert F. Kennedy Jr. withdrew from the ballot in Arizona late Thursday, a day before he and Donald Trump were set to appear miles apart in the Phoenix area as speculation grows that Kennedy could drop his independent presidential bid and endorse the Republican nominee.

item.title: The Rise of the Faux Libertarians
item.description: The Democrats are leaning into the freedom to mislead.

item.title: Can This Grassroot Group’s Ballot-Chasing Efforts Help Turn Nevada Red This November?
item.description: The Sun City Summerlin Conservatives Club is seeking to give Democrats' ballot-chasing operation a run for its money this November.

item.title: 27 states press SCOTUS to halt Biden ATF’s 'blatant attack' on gun owners, claiming end-run around Congress
item.description: West Virginia and Montana led 27 states in filing an amicus brief opposing the ATF's new rule expanding the definition of what a gun is.

item.title: Throngs chant 'Killer Kamala' outside convention as Harris delivers her big speech
item.description: CHICAGO -- Thousands of pro-Palestinian protesters demonstrated on the west side of Chicago and marched through the streets on the final night of the Democratic National Convention.

item.title: The Biden-Harris Administration Won’t Leave Women’s Sports Alone
item.description: Recent changes to Title IX threaten to sacrifice decades of progress in female athletics to woke politics masquerading as inclusivity.

item.title: Everyone Is Better Off When People Make Marriage And Family A Priority
item.description: Half of Americans say they don’t want to go anywhere near those disgusting vacay-blockers who will someday fund their government entitlements.

item.title: 'Access granted': Biden's free vacation at friend's California mansion draws ire of critics
item.description: President Biden wants to establish Supreme Court ethics rules, but the lame-duck president has his own history of accepting gifts from powerful and wealthy friends.

item.title: Former Rep. Adam Kinzinger calls Trump a 'weak man pretending to be strong'
item.description: Republican former Rep. Adam Kinzinger attacked his longtime foe, GOP nominee Donald Trump, as a "weak man" Thursday night in a speech to the Democratic National Convention.

item.title: Red Island Remembers Western History without Guilt
item.description: Robin Campillo confronts innocence and revolution.

item.title: Christian Classical Schools Deserve A Hymnody As Good As Their Grammar And History
item.description: A Christian can absorb far more theology through singing classic hymns in weekly worship than through academic study.
